{"tid":1427501,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高斯尼除阿仙奴波衫惹眾怒","createTime":"2019-08-07T06:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T08:29:56.000Z","uid":153600,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d144ec4b6e3676225b5ad97a7ee79e7a703b2a84","tid":1427501,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:27:57.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】阿仙奴前隊長高斯尼透過短片宣佈加盟波爾多，但宣傳片卻引起阿仙奴球迷大怒。<br />\n<br />\n法國中堅高斯尼（Laurent Koscielny）周二以460萬英鎊的轉會費，結束效力9年的阿仙奴加盟波爾多。他今夏因轉會缺席球隊季前備戰，因此與阿仙奴關係決裂。波爾多為高斯尼的加盟短片中，就出現令阿仙奴球迷十分憤怒的鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n高斯尼在片段中，把阿仙奴球衣脫掉露出内內的波爾多戰衣。阿仙奴球迷紛紛留言表達不滿，Robert Magee寫道：「一點也不尊重阿仙奴！是我見過對阿仙奴最不尊重的行為。」<br />\n<br />\n另一個粉絲寫道：「你不該這樣對待阿仙奴球衣，我真對你失望透頂了，非常不尊重。」高斯尼可以跟會方不滿，但不尊重球迷則是十分愚蠢的。<br />\n<br />\n相關片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ktkgnv5KPJM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dktkgnv5KPJM&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=5cba5266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ktkgnv5KPJM</a>"},{"pid":"f045492ab0910c018582edc6b19db56fc4568634","tid":1427501,"uid":78336,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:29:03.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴球迷同中國人有咩分別"},{"pid":"20ddba3073c61700b3d41b6ed821a923edea68e7","tid":1427501,"uid":82268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"串到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d471527bf2e145ba93afd667046133e8839f48","tid":1427501,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f045492ab0910c018582edc6b19db56fc4568634","tid":1427501,"uid":78336,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:29:03.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴球迷同中國人有咩分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e3e5ee820e6f7af0242055ed6a4c550dd6b6d0","tid":1427501,"uid":166474,"like":15,"dislike":0,"sco